let status = {
    temp_Outer : "",
    temp_Inner : "",
    humid_Outer : "",
    humid_Inner : "",
    pm10_Outer : "",
    pm10_Inner : "",
    pm25_Outer : "",
    pm25_Inner : "",
    voc_Outer : "",
    voc_Inner : "",
    co2_Outer : "",
    co2_Inner : "",
    year : "",
    month : "",
    date : "",
    hours : "",
    minute : "", 
    second : "",
    aircleanermode : "",
    aircleanerspeed : "",
    timestamp : ""
};


module.exports = status;

const mongoose = require('mongoose');
const sensor_Schema = new mongoose.Schema({
    id : String,
    temp: Number,
    humid : Number,
    pm25: Number,
    pm10: Number,
    voc: Number,
    co2: Number,
    year: Number,
    month: Number,
    date: Number,
    hours: Number,
    minute: Number,
    second: Number,
    aircleanermode : Number,
    aircleanerspeed: Number,
    timestamp: Number
});


module.exports = mongoose.model('Inner',sensor_Schema,'Inner');
